name: DREAM416158621.09
description:
The soft, sand-like meltdown marks its presence upon the vulcanic surface.
Unshaped everchanging spectres float around the entrance of the cave, with theyr
flamingo coloured existance. Somewhere, somehow, denser than before. Many different
concentrations of gravity make up another intrusion of dimension. It materializes just
enough of it's own body to integrate within the eco-system. A thin lilac myst revolves
around the solids and unsolids, creating a infinite stillnes within movement. The window to time shuts and re-shuttles like small mecanisms of organization. 

2480 x 3508 Dreamscroll.
